  "instructions": [
    "Place flour and water/broth in a saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Stir until smooth, then add rendered fat and continue to stir.",
    "Simmer for about 5 minutes or until the mixture begins to char and thicken.",
    "Gradually stir in salt and pepper until evenly distributed.",
    "Transfer the pilaf into a donabe dish which will help maintain heat during serving.",
    "Serve warm as a side dish or appetizer."
